{"tid":2246883,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"一人一個最真實撞鬼經歷","createTime":"2020-10-17T12:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T22:36:58.000Z","uid":353278,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17c1c47d1eb138ff611f704ffaafd7900d5274f8","tid":2246883,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"十幾歲, 瞓瞓下瞓醒咗, 之後聽到有個女人叫我個名<br />\n&quot;XX 你出嚟啦, XX 你出嚟啦, XX 你出嚟啦.....&quot;<br />\n嗰把聲係同時由窗出面, 由門口出面傳嚟, 非常立體聲!<br />\n嚇到我瞓咗喺度完全唔敢喐, 嗰一刻係非常清醒<br />\n之後把聲冇咗我先敢瞓"},{"pid":"6062a21e78352c979fa3142f6ea20adcc72e042e","tid":2246883,"uid":179867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18c7ecc8d16d430f4cc4d1396ade11c6d883ce1","tid":2246883,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6062a21e78352c979fa3142f6ea20adcc72e042e","tid":2246883,"uid":179867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"係叫我個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7ae7194d3777639bc25dedb9de31688a490ed2","tid":2246883,"uid":179867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b18c7ecc8d16d430f4cc4d1396ade11c6d883ce1","tid":2246883,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6062a21e78352c979fa3142f6ea20adcc72e042e","tid":2246883,"uid":179867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"係叫我個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76335107bfb4c7eb7b033aa1255c0e67d0e57a3","tid":