822f","tid":2246883,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bebac7bc00c91bf5828fa3820c91d8d3d0f2bd2f","tid":2246883,"uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"最真實撞鬼經歷︰<br />\n<br />\n仲見到吉田之寶係連登"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"你做乜追蹤我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"你做乜跟蹤我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf92b0d4c133d9d392c9cf141c876038b1dd2d22","tid":2246883,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"肚痛去緊廁所嗰陣見到門罅突然之間有一個光影閃過<br />\n但係屋企得我自己一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚咗一陣之後就索性當係簷蛇跑過會安心啲"},{"pid":"cea8670371d401c3c23cf7bb6f6e456fedc3d089","tid":2246883,"uid":141237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"細個屋企大廳仲有果d鐵籠式陽台，係一個長方體凸出去，咁中間就擺左個類似神主牌咁既座係度，有日唔知做乜我坐左上去個鐵籠度背住陽台出面咁坐左響度，突然就有隻手唔記得係拍左我一下定推左我一下背脊，果陣雖然唔識鬼神嘢，但係果下陌生既感覺有d不安於是跳返落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0705fd6bb3ac680941348e9e81719982e9d7e2ca","tid":2246883,"uid":244113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:48:38.000Z","msg":"大一嗰時，有次番屋企要上樓梯，見到條千年蜈蚣爬緊入隔離塊空地<br />\nSize都唔知有幾多個人咁大，見唔到頭尾，一級樓梯咁闊，啲腳又長又尖，慢慢咁隊落地發出啲喀喀聲<br />\n最後頭也不回咁急急腳走咗，隔咗一陣再番去就乜都睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n俾我再見到佢一定會捐入塊空地跟佢尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4044fc270a721932fd91f24f0cbe76c134ab7658","tid":2246883,"uid":357705,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"有次去旅行，上到某商場第三樓突然有股力場當係前面，完全無辦法向前行... <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJEcAR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJEcAR3.jpg&h=e264704f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個商場嗰層特別吉...<br />\n事後朋友話有鬼想上我身"},{"pid":"e9fd2c6890cd27cf8bf273ee6f07dc36631a8aa2","tid":2246883,"uid":335834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4044fc270a721932fd91f24f0cbe76c134ab7658","tid":2246883,"uid":357705,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"有次去旅行，上到某商場第三樓突然有股力場當係前面，完全無辦法向前行... <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJEcAR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJEcAR3.jpg&h=e264704f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個商場嗰層特別吉...<br />\n事後朋友話有鬼想上我身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T22:36:58.000Z","msg":"Feel到吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知d野喎"}]}